About
An icon of the city skyline, this high-altitude attraction is located 46 stories up and is a half scale replica of the world-famous Paris, France landmark. Rise above the frenzy of the Strip at one of Paris Las Vegasâ€™ premier attractions with amazing views. Known as one of the most romantic spots in Las Vegas, this is a must-see attraction.
